Title: Scooby-Doo on Zombie Island
Genre: Animation, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Mystery
Director: Hiroshi Aoyama, Kazumi Fukushima, Jim Stenstrum
Writer: Davis Doi (story), Glenn Leopold (story), Glenn Leopold (screenplay), William Hanna (characters), Joseph Barbera (characters)
Actors: Scott Innes, Billy West, Mary Kay Bergman, Frank Welker
Plot: The Mystery Gang reunite and visit Moonscar Island, a remote island with a dark secret. Daphne wants more than just a villain in a costume, and they get more than they ever expected.
